"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/772278","Ministry of Justice","false","2017-10-23","<p>HM Courts &amp; Tribunals Service does not centrally collect information on the number of claimants in Glasgow East constituency. Personal data for Employment Tribunal cases are archived 12 months after a case is concluded.</p>","Esher and Walton","Dominic Raab",,"2017-10-23T15:04:58.363Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/772278/answer","Biography information for Dominic Raab","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/772278/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/772278/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2017-10-17","Employment Tribunals Service: Glasgow East","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many employment tribunal claimants there were in Glasgow East constituency in the 12 months (a) before and (b) after the introduction of tribunal fees.","false","Biography information for David Linden","Glasgow East","David Linden","108089"
